#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:340
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\pagebreak\n"
"\\pagetarget{Specialty}{\\subheader{Hero Specialty Cards}}\n"
"\\index{Hero Specialty card}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\pagebreak\n"
"\\pagetarget{Specialty}{\\subheader{Karty Specjalności Bohatera}}\n"
"\\index{Karta!Specjalności Bohatera}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:345
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Hero Specialty cards\\index{Specialty cards} are gained from \\pagelink{Level}{Level ups}.\n"
"Each Main Hero has a unique set of Specialty cards.\n"
"While some of these cards have effects which resemble Spell cards and even make use of \\svg{empower}, Specialty cards are their \\textbf{own unique category of cards}.\n"
"For example, the limit of 1 Spell per Combat Round doesn't apply to Specialty cards.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Karty Specjalności Bohatera\\index{Karta!Specjalności} są pozyskiwane podczas \\pagelink{Level}{zdobywania Poziomów}.\n"
"Każdy Bohater Główny ma unikalny zestaw kart Specjalności.\n"
"Mimo że niektóre z~tych Kart mają efekty podobne do Kart Zaklęć i~nawet wykorzystują \\svg{empower}, Karty Specjalności są \\textbf{unikalną kategorią kart}.\n"
"Przykładowo limit jednego Zaklęcia na Rundę Walki nie dotyczy kart Specjalności.\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:353
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{\\cards/specialty.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\footnotesize\\textit{A Level IV Specialty card, belonging to Catherine the Knight.}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{translations/assets/pl/cards/specialty.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\footnotesize\\textit{Karta Specjalności IV Poziomu Rycerza Katarzyny.}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:361
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{\\cards/specialty2.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\footnotesize\\textit{A Level I Specialty card, belonging to Deemer the Warlock. It uses \\svg{empower}, but does NOT belong to any School of Magic, despite the imagery.}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{translations/assets/pl/specialty2.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\footnotesize\\textit{Karta Specjalności I Poziomu Czarnoksiężnika Deemera. Wykorzystuje \\svg{empower}, ale \\textbf{nie należy} do żadnej Szkoły Magii, pomimo grafiki.}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:364
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\columnbreak\n"
"\\pagetarget{Artifact}{\\subheader{Artifact Cards}}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\columnbreak\n"
"\\pagetarget{Artifact}{\\subheader{Karty Artefaktów}}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:371
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Artifact cards\\index{Artifact cards} have a top and bottom effect. When you play one, you must \\textbf{choose which effect} you are using.\n"
"They are divided into 3 Levels: Minor, Major, and Relic, with different border color.\n"
"These Levels relate to the overall Power of the card and may be referenced when resolving certain effects or during Scenario setup.\n"
"Otherwise, all Artifact cards are normally shuffled together to form the Artifact Deck regardless of their Level.\n"
"They are gained through map exploration.\\par\n"
"Artifacts can be \\pagelink{Trading}{traded} in Alliance and Cooperative Scenarios.\\par\n"
"\\begin{tikzpicture}\n"
msgstr ""
"Karty Artefaktów\\index{Karta!Artefaktu} mają górny oraz dolny efekt. Gdy je zagrywasz, musisz \\textbf{wybrać efekt}, którego używasz.\n"
"Dzielą się one na 3 Poziomy: Słabe, Mocne oraz Relikty, różniące się kolorem ramki.\n"
"Te poziomy odnoszą się do ogólnej Siły Karty, a~dodatkowo mogą być wskazane podczas rozgrywania niektórych efektów lub podczas przygotowania Scenariusza.\n"
"Jeżeli w~Scenariuszu nie podano inaczej, wszystkie Karty Artefaktów są tasowane razem, aby stworzyć Talię Artefaktów bez względu na ich Poziom.\n"
"Można je zdobywać podczas odkrywania mapy.\n"
"Artefakty mogą być \\pagelink{Trading}{wymieniane} w~Trybie Sojuszu oraz Kooperacji.\\par\n"
"\\begin{tikzpicture}\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:391
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\node (major) {\\includegraphics[width=0.6\\linewidth]{\\cards/artifact.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{major}\n"
"    \\draw (0.2, 0.8) node {\\encircle{1}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.7, 0.4) node {\\encircle{2}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.9, 0.9) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.25, 0.2) node {\\encircle{4}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"  \\node [below=0pt of major.south] {\\imagecaption{Major Artifact}};\n"
"  \\node (relic) [right=0.05\\linewidth of major.south east, anchor=south west] {\\includegraphics[width=0.3\\linewidth]{\\cards/relic_artifact.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{relic}\n"
"    \\draw (0.5, 0.7) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\node [below=0pt of relic.south] {\\imagecaption{Relic Artifact}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"  \\node (minor) [above=4em of relic.north] {\\includegraphics[width=0.3\\linewidth]{\\cards/minor_artifact.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{minor}\n"
"    \\draw (0.5, 0.7) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\node [below=0pt of minor.south] {\\imagecaption{Minor Artifact}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"\\end{tikzpicture}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\node (major) {\\includegraphics[width=0.6\\linewidth]{translations/assets/pl/cards/artifact.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{major}\n"
"    \\draw (0.2, 0.8) node {\\encircle{1}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.7, 0.4) node {\\encircle{2}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.9, 0.9) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.25, 0.2) node {\\encircle{4}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"  \\node [below=0pt of major.south] {\\imagecaption{Mocny Artefakt}};\n"
"  \\node (relic) [right=0.05\\linewidth of major.south east, anchor=south west] {\\includegraphics[width=0.3\\linewidth]{\\cards/relic_artifact.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{relic}\n"
"    \\draw (0.5, 0.7) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\node [below=0pt of relic.south] {\\imagecaption{Relikt}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"  \\node (minor) [above=4em of relic.north] {\\includegraphics[width=0.3\\linewidth]{\\cards/minor_artifact.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{minor}\n"
"    \\draw (0.5, 0.7) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\node [below=0pt of minor.south] {\\imagecaption{Słaby Artefakt}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"\\end{tikzpicture}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:401
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\begin{multicols}{2}\n"
"  \\footnotesize\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{1.}] Name\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{2.}] Effect\n"
"    \\columnbreak\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{3.}] Level\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{4.}] Flavor text\n"
"  \\end{itemize}"
msgstr ""
"\\begin{multicols}{2}\n"
"  \\footnotesize\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{1.}] Nazwa\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{2.}] Efekt\n"
"    \\columnbreak\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{3.}] Poziom\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{4.}] Tekst fabularny\n"
"  \\end{itemize}"

#. type: center
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:408
msgid ""
"{\\transparent{0.2}\\includegraphics[width=0.9\\linewidth]{\\art/"
"diplomats_ring.png}}"
msgstr ""
"{\\transparent{0.2}\\includegraphics[width=0.8\\linewidth]{\\art/"
"diplomats_ring.png}}"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:413
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{stronghold}\n"
"\\pagetarget{Spell Scroll Cards}{\\subheader{Spell Scroll Cards}}\\index{Spell Scroll cards}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{stronghold}\n"
"\\pagetarget{Spell Scroll Cards}{\\subheader{Karty Pergaminów z~Zaklęciami}}\\index{Karta!Pergaminu z~Zaklęciami}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:418
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"During setup shuffle 10 of the Spell Scroll cards into the Artifact Deck.\n"
"Set the remaining 10 cards aside to form a Spell Scroll Deck.\n"
"Some locations or Scenario effects may call for them later.\n"
"\\vspace*{1em}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Podczas przygotowania wtasuj 10 Kart Pergaminów z~Zaklęciami do Talii Artefaktów.\n"
"Pozostałe 10 kart odłóż na bok, tworząc Talię Pergaminów z~Zaklęciami.\n"
"Niektóre lokacje lub Scenariusze mogą ich później wymagać.\n"
"\\vspace*{0.7em}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:428
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{\\cards/spell_scroll.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\begin{center}\n"
"         \\imagecaption{Spell Scroll card}\n"
"    \\end{center}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{translations/assets/pl/cards/spell_scroll.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\begin{center}\n"
"         \\imagecaption{Karta Pergaminu z~Zaklęciami}\n"
"    \\end{center}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:434
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\vspace*{1em}\n"
"When you gain a Spell Scroll, place it next to your Hero Board, take the two top cards from the Spell Deck and place them face-down on the Spell Scroll.\n"
"You can look at these Spells at any time and they don't count toward your Hand \\svg{hand} Limit.\n"
"You can only have two Spell Scrolls at a time.\n"
"If you gain a third one, draw the new Spells normally and then decide whether to discard the newly gained Spell Scroll or replace one you already have (including all Spells on it).\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\vspace*{0.7em}\n"
"Gdy zdobywasz Pergamin, połóż go obok swojej Planszetki Bohatera, weź dwie wierzchnie karty z~Talii Zaklęć i~połóż je zakryte na Pergaminie.\n"
"Możesz oglądać te Zaklęcia w~dowolnym momencie. Nie liczą się one do twojego limitu kart \\svg{hand} na ręce.\n"
"Jednocześnie możesz mieć tylko dwa Pergaminy.\n"
"Jeśli zdobędziesz trzeci, dobierz nowe Zaklęcia normalnie, a~następnie zdecyduj, czy odrzucić nowo zdobyty Pergamin, czy zastąpić nim jeden z~posiadanych (wraz ze wszystkimi Zaklęciami na nim).\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:444
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You can play Spells from a Spell Scroll like any other Spell with the following exceptions:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item They don't count towards your Spell Limit.\n"
"    You can also play a Spell from your hand during this Combat Round.\n"
"    \\item You may use the Spell's \\textbf{lowest Power} \\svg{empower} \\textbf{effect}, without needing to pay its cost (e.g. in case of \\wikilink{spells/implosion}{Implosion} the cost is 1).\n"
"      You can't Empower the Spell with \\svg{empower} from any source.\n"
"\\end{itemize}"
msgstr ""
"Zaklęcia z~Pergaminu możesz zagrywać jak inne Zaklęcia, z~następującymi wyjątkami:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item Nie liczą się one do twojego limitu Zaklęć.\n"
"    W~danej Rundzie Walki możesz dodatkowo zagrać Zaklęcie z~ręki.\n"
"    \\item Możesz użyć \\textbf{efektu} Zaklęcia o~\\textbf{najniższej Mocy} \\svg{empower}, bez płacenia jego kosztu (np. dla \\wikilink{spells/implosion}{Implozji} koszt wynosi 1).\n"
"      Nie możesz wzmocnić tego Zaklęcia za pomocą \\svg{empower} z~żadnego źródła.\n"
"\\end{itemize}"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:452
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{stronghold}\n"
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item They can't be used to increase the \\svg{empower} of another Spell.\n"
"    \\item You can \\pagelink{selling Spell Scrolls}{sell Spell Scrolls} at a Trading Post for 2 \\svg{gold} per each Spell on it.\n"
"    \\item After using or selling those Spells, the Spell card is \\textbf{removed}, not discarded.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{stronghold}\n"
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item Nie można ich użyć do zwiększenia \\svg{empower} innego Zaklęcia.\n"
"    \\item Możesz \\pagelink{selling Spell Scrolls}{sprzedać Pergaminy z~Zaklęciami} w~Punkcie Handlowym za 2~\\svg{gold} za każde Zaklęcie na nim.\n"
"    \\item Po zagraniu albo sprzedaniu karta Zaklęcia jest \\textbf{usuwana}, a~nie odrzucana.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:454
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If the last Spell on a Spell Scroll is used or sold, place the Spell Scroll back in its Deck.\n"
"\n"
msgstr "Jeśli ostatnie Zaklęcie na Pergaminie z~Zaklęciami zostanie użyte lub sprzedane, odłóż Pergamin z~powrotem do jego Talii.\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:457
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\medskip\n"
"Spell Scrolls are not part of your Deck, therefore they are not carried over between Scenarios in a Campaign."
msgstr "Pergaminy nie są częścią twojej Talii, więc nie możesz ich przenieść między Scenariuszami w~Kampanii."

